app-example

# Firebase service-account credentials — NEVER commit. These grant
# admin-level access to the Firebase project. Upload to EAS via
# `npx eas credentials` and keep the JSON outside source control.
#
# Firebase Cloud Messaging has been REMOVED from this build (user request,
# 2026-05-11). `google-services.json` is no longer needed. We list it here
# so a stale local copy doesn't accidentally get re-committed.
google-services.json
firebase-service-account*.json
GoogleService-Info.plist
*-firebase-adminsdk-*.json
